author: jleroux
msg: Fixes "Some fields are missing in the person simple-map-processor" https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-6357

After some additions on the Person entity definition the person simple-map-processor has not been updated. I stumbled upon it while missing occupation. I though noticed some has been introduced in the validateCustomerInfo in ecommerce. This completes the person simple-map-processor, no fields are missing.
